### 4-5: case "call" 검증 추가 (줄 441 직후)

```typescript
// 인자 타입 검증 루프 후, return fnType.returnType 전에 삽입:

// [Phase 6] Capability Propagation 검증
// Strict: callee.capabilities ⊆ caller.capabilities
if (fnType.capabilities && fnType.capabilities.length > 0) {
  for (const required of fnType.capabilities) {
    const callerHas = this.currentCapabilities.some(
      c => c.cap === required.cap &&
           this.capabilityCovers(c, required)
    )
    if (!callerHas) {
      this.addError(
        `Call to '${fnName}' requires capability '${required.cap}' ` +
        `${required.arg ? `(${required.arg})` : ""}, ` +
        `but caller does not declare it`,
        undefined, undefined
      )
    }
  }
}
```

### 4-6: capabilityCovers() 헬퍼 추가

Path prefix 매칭 + network wildcard 처리:

```typescript
private capabilityCovers(caller: Capability, callee: Capability): boolean {
  if (caller.cap !== callee.cap) return false
  if (!callee.arg) return true   // callee가 경로 무관하면 OK
  if (!caller.arg) return false  // caller가 무제한인데 callee가 제한적? 아니, 이 경우는 OK

  // Path: /tmp → /tmp/file.txt OK, /tmp → /etc NG
  if (caller.cap === "read_file" || caller.cap === "write_file") {
    return this.pathIsUnder(callee.arg, caller.arg)
  }

  // Network: api.openai.com → api.openai.com OK, *.openai.com → sub.openai.com OK
  if (caller.cap === "network") {
    return this.hostMatches(callee.arg, caller.arg)
  }

  return caller.arg === callee.arg
}

private pathIsUnder(target: string, allowedPrefix: string): boolean {
  // ".." 즉시 거부
  if (target.includes("..")) return false
  const normalized = target.replace(/\/+/g, "/").replace(/\/$/, "")
  const prefix = allowedPrefix.replace(/\/+/g, "/").replace(/\/$/, "")
  return normalized === prefix || normalized.startsWith(prefix + "/")
}

private hostMatches(target: string, pattern: string): boolean {
  if (pattern === target) return true
  if (pattern.startsWith("*.")) {
    const base = pattern.slice(2)
    return target.endsWith("." + base) && !target.slice(0, -base.length - 1).includes(".")
  }
  return false
}
```

### 4-7: Built-in 호출 검증 (case "call" 확장)

내장 함수(file.read 등) 호출 시 capability 검증:

```typescript
// case "call" 초반에 built-in 검증 추가
const builtinRequired = this.BUILTIN_REQUIRED_CAPABILITIES.get(fnName)
if (builtinRequired) {
  const callerHas = this.currentCapabilities.some(c => c.cap === builtinRequired)
  if (!callerHas) {
    this.addError(
      `'${fnName}' requires capability '${builtinRequired}', not declared`,
      undefined, undefined
    )
  }
}
```

